🔍 Detection Queries

🔹 Failed Login Detection
index=main "Failed password"

🔹 Extract IP + User
index=main "Failed password"
| rex "from (?<src>\S+)"
| rex "Failed password for (?:invalid user )?(?<user>\S+)"
| stats count by src, user
| sort -count

🔹 Brute Force Detection Rule
index=main "Failed password"
| rex "from (?<src>\S+)"
| stats count by src
| where count > 5

